{
    "title": "Entertainment vs. Transformation",
    "description": "Distinguishing cyberdelic VR from entertainment/gaming VR by understanding purpose and attention direction.",
    "theme": {
        "primaryColor": "#5900ff",
        "fontBody": "Rajdhani, sans-serif"
    },
    "modules": [
        {
            "id": "entertainment_pd_3.1",
            "title": "Same Technology, Different Worlds",
            "type": "progressive-disclosure",
            "content": {
                "sections": [
                    {
                        "title": "Same Technology, Different Worlds",
                        "content": "<p>Not all VR is cyberdelic. Most VR is entertainment. What determines the category isn't the hardware—headsets are neutral—but the purpose behind the design.</p>",
                        "triggerLabel": "Direction of Attention"
                    },
                    {
                        "title": "The Direction of Attention",
                        "media": {
                            "type": "image",
                            "src": "../assets/images/module1/lesson3/attention_flow.jpg",
                            "alt": "Diagram: Outward attention (Entertainment) vs Inward attention (Cyberdelic)"
                        },
                        "mediaLayout": "left",
                        "content": "<p><strong>Entertainment VR</strong> directs attention outward into fantasy, narrative, or stimulation. You engage with external content.<br><br><strong>Cyberdelic VR</strong> directs attention inward toward awareness itself. You explore your own consciousness.</p>",
                        "triggerLabel": "Questions We Ask"
                    },
                    {
                        "title": "Entertainment Asks: What Can I Experience?",
                        "content": "<p>Entertainment VR focuses on novelty and excitement: \"What world can I explore? What adventure can I have?\" It's about external engagement.</p>",
                        "triggerLabel": "Cyberdelics Asks"
                    },
                    {
                        "title": "Cyberdelics Asks: What Can I Discover?",
                        "content": "<p>Cyberdelic VR focuses on awareness and transformation: \"What patterns exist in my mind? How do I relate to experience?\" The environment serves inner discovery.</p>",
                        "triggerLabel": "Different Needs"
                    },
                    {
                        "title": "Not Better or Worse, Just Different",
                        "content": "<p>Entertainment offers joy and fun. Cyberdelics offer growth and insight. Neither is superior; they serve different human needs. Key takeaway: Know which one you're engaging with.</p>",
                        "triggerLabel": "Test Your Eye"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
