                            "q1_c": "<p>Incorrect. Biofeedback is common but not required.</p>",
                            "q1_d": "<p>Incorrect. Slower pace is common but not a defining factor.</p>",
                            "q1_b": "<p>✓ Correct!</p><p>Direction of attention (inward vs. outward) and purpose (transformation vs. entertainment) are the primary differentiators.</p>"
